    <h2>Program Details | Detalles del Programa</h2>
    <p>
        Ella Rises provides a safe, supportive environment for our participants to engage in enriching activities.
        By signing this form, you grant permission for your child to participate in our programs and activities,
        including field trips, workshops, and other planned events.
        <br><br>
        Ella Rises ofrece un entorno seguro y de apoyo para que las participantes participen en actividades enriquecedoras.
        Al firmar este formulario, usted otorga permiso para que su hija participe en todas las actividades del programa,
        incluyendo excursiones, talleres y otros eventos planificados.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <!-- Parent/Guardian Info -->
    <label>Parent/Guardian Name | Nombre del Padre/Madre/Tutor *</label>
    <input type="text" name="parent_name" required>

    <label>Phone Number | Número de teléfono *</label>
    <input type="tel" name="parent_phone" required>

    <label>Parent Email Address | Correo electrónico de los padres *</label>
    <input type="email" name="parent_email" required>

    <!-- Participant Info -->
    <label>Participant Name | Nombre de Participante *</label>
    <input type="text" name="participant_name" required>

    <label>Child's Date of Birth | Fecha de Nacimiento de su Hija *</label>
    <input type="date" name="dob" required>

    <label>Date *</label>
    <input type="date" name="form_date" required>

    <label>Grade | Año Escolar *</label>
    <input type="text" name="grade" required>

    <label>What school does the student attend? | ¿A qué escuela asiste su hija? *</label>
    <input type="text" name="school" required>

    <hr>

    <!-- Program Selection -->
    <label>
        Which program(s) are you interested in participating in? *
        <br>¿En cuál(es) programas desea participar?
        <br><small>*University tours and other educational initiatives are automatically shared with all participants.</small>
        <br><small>Visitas universitarias y otras iniciativas educativas se comparten automáticamente con todas nuestras participantes.</small>
    </label>

    <div class="checkbox-group">
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="programs[]" value="Mariachi" required> Mariachi (waitlist)</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="programs[]" value="Ballet Folklorico"> Ballet Folklórico</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="programs[]" value="Art"> Art | Arte</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="programs[]" value="STEM"> STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Math)</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="programs[]" value="Summer Camps"> Summer Day Camps | Campamentos de Verano</label>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- Mariachi Instrument -->
    <label>
        Regarding mariachi: which instrument is your daughter interested in? *
        <br>Con respecto al mariachi: ¿Cuál instrumento desea su hija aprender?
    </label>

    <select name="mariachi_instrument" required>
        <option value="">-- Select / Seleccione --</option>
        <option value="Violin">Violin</option>
        <option value="Guitar">Guitar | Guitarra</option>
        <option value="Trumpet">Trumpet | Trompeta</option>
        <option value="Guitarron">Guitarron</option>
        <option value="Vihuela">Vihuela</option>
    </select>

    <label>
        If your daughter already plays an instrument, what does she play and for how long? *
        <br>Si su hija ya toca un instrumento, ¿cuál toca y cuánto tiempo lleva tocándolo?
    </label>
    <input type="text" name="instrument_experience" required>

    <hr>

    <!-- Registration Fee -->
    <label>
        Registration Fee (Annual $45) | Cuota de inscripción anual ($45) *
        <br>Scholarships available for families in need | Becas disponibles
    </label>

    <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="registration_fee" value="Can pay" required> Yes, we can pay the registration fee. | Sí</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="registration_fee" value="Apply scholarship"> I would like to apply for a scholarship. | Quiero aplicar para una beca.</label>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- Monthly Tuition -->
    <label>
        Beginning May 1, 2026: monthly tuition $35 per student *
        <br>A partir del 1 de mayo de 2026: matrícula mensual de $35 por estudiante
    </label>

    <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="monthly_tuition_ack" value="Yes" required> I understand. | Entiendo.</label>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- Language Preference -->
    <label>Language preference for reminders | Preferencia de idioma *</label>

    <select name="language_preference" required>
        <option value="">-- Select / Seleccione --</option>
        <option value="English">English | Inglés</option>
        <option value="Spanish">Spanish | Español</option>
        <option value="No preference">No preference | No tengo preferencia</option>
        <option value="Other">Other Language | Otro idioma</option>
    </select>

    <hr>

    <!-- Emergency Medical Consent -->
    <label>Emergency Medical Consent | Consentimiento de emergencias médicas *</label>

    <div class="radio-group">
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="medical_consent" value="Yes" required>
            I authorize Ella Rises Foundation to seek medical attention if necessary.
            <br>
        </label>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- Photo & Video Consent -->
    <label>Photo & Video Consent | Consentimiento de fotos y videos *</label>

    <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="photo_consent" value="Yes" required> Yes, I give permission. | Sí, doy permiso.</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="photo_consent" value="No"> No, I do not give permission. | No, no doy permiso.</label>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- Agreement Paragraph -->
    <p>
        "I, the undersigned, hereby give permission for my child to participate in the Ella Rises Foundation After-School Program...
        <br><br>
    </p>

    <label>I agree. Estoy de acuerdo. *</label>
    <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="agreement" value="Agree" required> I agree. | Estoy de acuerdo.</label>
    </div>

    <label>Parent/Guardian Signature (type your name) | Firma del Padre/Madre/Tutor *</label>
    <input type="text" name="signature" required>

    <label>Date | Fecha *</label>
    <input type="date" name="signature_date" required>

    <div>
        <button type="submit">Create Account</button>
    </div>
</form>

</body>

</html>